# Simple React Express App

A Express + React project thhat gets the median of the primes numbers from the number limit. This is a test project. 


## Installation

Before installing, download and install Nodejs & make sure you are inside the project folder.

Install NPM packages using the below command.

```bash
npm install
```

For installing frontend packages, get to frontend folder then run the below code

```bash
npm install
```

## Run server Locally

Running below code.

```bash
npm run dev
```

## Run client Locally

Running below code from client folder.

```bash
npm start
```


## Testing

All test cases

```bash
npm test
```

